<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Text-to-image: AI image generation inside the Canva editor without switching platforms</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Magic Expand: Extend the borders of any image with AI-generated content matching the original</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Brand Kit: Lock in brand fonts, colors, and logos that apply automatically across designs</span></li>
