<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Custom avatars: Create a personalized AI presenter from your own video footage</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Branching video: Interactive videos where viewers navigate their own content path (2026 feature)</span></li>
