<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">Methodology: How VentureBurn Evaluated These Marketing Platforms</span></h2>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-203157 size-full" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/How-VentureBurn-Evaluated-These-Marketing-Platforms.jpg" alt="Methodology: How VentureBurn Evaluated These Marketing Platforms" width="2426" height="1728" /></p>
