<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Can my account be frozen? </span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Yes. Because the corporate platform maintains total control, they possess the complete power to freeze accounts, halt withdrawals, or seize funds if they suspect illegal activity. This is a critical factor to remember when researching what is CEX functionality.</span></p>
