<td><b>Ease of Use</b></td>
<td><b>Deployment</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Replit</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Full-stack + AI</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strong</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Very easy</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Instant</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
