<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Manual</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Codespaces</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cloud dev</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Moderate</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Moderate</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Good</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Cursor IDE</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Advanced devs</span></td>
