<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The AI voice generator market has moved fast over the past two years. What used to be a binary choice between robotic free tools and expensive studio software now spans a dozen platforms, each built around a different priority — realism, emotional range, business compliance, or pure cost. The picks above reflect testing across real scripts rather than polished demo clips, since that gap is where most platforms start to fall apart.</span></p>
<h2><b>Methodology: How VentureBurn Evaluated These Voice Tools</b></h2>
