<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every reputable gold dealers on this list holds an A+ BBB rating and has operated for multiple years with documented customer reviews. According to </span><a href="https://www.goldinvestinghub.com/best/best-place-to-buy-gold-online-top-7-dealers-reviewed-by-premiums-security/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Gold Investing Hub&#8217;s scam prevention guide</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, a verifiable physical address (not a PO box), a documented operating history of at least three years, and a minimum of several hundred verified customer reviews are the baseline checks for any best gold dealers you consider.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Be Cautious of Free Silver Offers and Excessive Markups</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Many best gold IRA dealers market themselves with offers of free silver for new accounts. According to </span><a href="https://www.goldinvestinghub.com/best/best-place-to-buy-gold-online-top-7-dealers-reviewed-by-premiums-security/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Gold Investing Hub&#8217;s analysis</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, these promotions frequently offset the value of the free silver through higher markups on the gold products you actually buy. Always calculate the total cost including premium before accepting any promotional offer from a best gold dealers online platform.</span></p>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Avoid Wire-Transfer-Only Dealers with No Track Record</span></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Legitimate best online gold dealers accept multiple payment methods and use insured, trackable shipping carriers. Any dealer that demands wire transfer only, has no published BBB profile, or cannot provide a documented delivery track record should be avoided. The best online bullion dealers on this list use FedEx or UPS with full insurance and require signature on delivery.</span></p>
